<html
  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
  xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
  xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
  xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
  xml:lang="en"
  lang="en"
  dir="ltr"
  metal:use-macro="context/@@main_template/master"
  i18n:domain="launchpad"
>
  <body>

<metal:portlets fill-slot="portlets">
  <tal:lifecycle replace="structure context/@@+portlet-lifecycle" />
  <tal:lifecycle replace="structure context/@@+portlet-related-questions" />
</metal:portlets>

<div metal:fill-slot="main">

    <h1 tal:content="context/title">FAQ Title</h1>

    <div id="faq-keywords"><b>Keywords: </b>
        <tal:keywords content="context/keywords">keywords</tal:keywords>
    </div>

    <div id="faq-content"
         tal:condition="context/content"
         tal:content="structure context/content/fmt:text-to-html">Content</div>
</div>

  <metal:help fill-slot="help">
    <p>FAQ documents contain a solution to a common problem (usually a question
      that appears often in the Answer Tracker.
    </p>
    <p>Project owners and answer contacts can modify FAQ documents by using
      the <b>Edit FAQ</b> menu item.
    </p>
    <p>The list of questions answered by this document can be found under
      in the <b>Related questions</b> portlet.
    </p>
  </metal:help>
</body>
</html>

